⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Cyan Garamonde
node FF6 · FF6 · ⟦Cyan Garamonde:FF6:fec6fb⟧

WHO   — Cyan Garamonde — the samurai retainer
WHAT  — A playable hero of Final Fantasy VI — Doma's last knight, who fights the Empire with the disciplined SwdTech of Bushido and carries the sorrow of a slaughtered home through the breaking of the world.
WHERE — FF6 · Final Fantasy VI  Framework inputs: Final Fantasy VI (America's Final Fantasy III, 1994)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because honor outlives the kingdom it was sworn to; because grief, unfaced, becomes a phantom that devours the living; because a man who has lost everything must still choose whether to follow his dead or stay among the living and fight for them.
HOW   — By the mastery of Bushido and the SwdTech of his blade, by a courtly honor that never bends, and by the long, painful courage to journey into his own dreams and let his beloved dead finally rest.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  My king, my wife, my son — all taken. I am the last blade of Doma, and I will carry your memory until grief itself bows to my honor.

